../tevm-monorepo/bundler-packages/solc/scripts/version/README.md:   - Add the new version to the `Releases` type if necessary
../tevm-monorepo/bundler-packages/solc/scripts/version/README.md:   - Add the new version to the `releases` object
../tevm-monorepo/bundler-packages/solc/scripts/version/README.md:   - Update the `solc` dependency to the new version
