../tevm-monorepo/bundler-packages/solc/scripts/version/README.md:2. Extract the version hash:
../tevm-monorepo/bundler-packages/solc/scripts/version/README.md:node -e "const solc = require('solc'); console.log(solc.version());"
../tevm-monorepo/bundler-packages/solc/scripts/version/README.md:4. Format the version hash as: `vx.y.z+commit.ab55807c.js` 
../tevm-monorepo/bundler-packages/solc/scripts/version/README.md:   (where `x.y.z` is the version number and `ab55807c` is the commit hash)
